
Hello all,

Recently, two entities that have executed Master Agreements with ENA merged.  
On July 9, 2000, Falcon Creek Resources, Inc., a Deleware Corporation merged 
with and into Sapient Energy Corp under the name of Sapient Energy Corp., a 
corporation organised and existing under the laws of the state of Delaware.

As we have executed Master Agreements with both entities, we should probably 
assign all of the deals confirmed under one contract to the other contract, 
terminate that other contract, and amend the credit terms of the remaining 
contract.

Termination
