Agreement
Contract we would like to terminate: Existing Sapient Energy Corporation 
Master Agreement


Assignment
Deals confirmed under the existing Sapient Energy Corporation contract that 
should be moved to the existing Falcon Creek Resources, Inc. Master Agreement:

NU3667.1
NU3667.2
