Amendment
The existing financial covenants of the Falcon Creek contract are acceptable 
as they were originally written.  I believe the only credit change needed 
would be to note that any reference to Falcon Creek should hence be 
recognised as Sapient Energy Corp.  I would appreciate some feedback on this.

Could we prepare a single document that would accomplish all of this or 
should we prepare two.  If we did prepare two documents, one would be an 
assignment/termination agreement and the other would be an amendment letter 
